android.car.projection

类 ProjectionStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.car.projection.ProjectionStatus

  • public final class ProjectionStatus
extends java.lang.Object
    This class encapsulates information about projection status and connected mobile devices.

    Since the number of connected devices expected to be small we include information about connected devices in every status update.
